metadata.name: ็็HUMAN ?
metadata.description: Human beings are high society and intellectual. It is different from wildlife with only instinct to survive. Nowadays, there are negative aspects of the society, such as persecution. exploit Trying to control too much freedom or control. All human beings in society have different status and roles. It also has the wisdom to choose to do things. Every society has good and bad people. If the human moral ethics in the life. It could be the worst crisis. So I brought these crushes. In addition to news from the print media. And the dystopia literature inspired inspiration in the creation of art. By creating a painting language series. By creating a symbol that we are familiar in everyday life. Create new contexts that give negative results. It shows the negative aspects of belief and personal attitudes. To communicate and stimulate moral and ethical behavior in the self.
